{"id":"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers","title":"RunGuardsAndResolvers","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers\", \"name\": \"RunGuardsAndResolvers\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/models.ts#L242-L267\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"runguardsandresolvers\">RunGuardsAndResolvers<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#runguardsandresolvers\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ek7dxho1xkkew0j03z87z9ae1\">何时在路由上运行警卫和解析器的策略。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers\" class=\"code-anchor\">RunGuardsAndResolvers</a> = 'pathParamsChange' | 'pathParamsOrQueryParamsChange' | 'paramsChange' | 'paramsOrQueryParamsChange' | 'always' | ((from: <a href=\"api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\" class=\"code-anchor\">ActivatedRouteSnapshot</a>, to: <a href=\"api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\" class=\"code-anchor\">ActivatedRouteSnapshot</a>) =&gt; boolean);\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/router/Route#runGuardsAndResolvers\"><code>Route#runGuardsAndResolvers</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e67odqzo31gi0yrb7yiv3a4s3\">激活或停用路由时，守卫和/或解析器将始终运行。当路由未更改时，默认行为与 <code>paramsChange</code> 相同。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6uqo2iwzvsn3er31yhkcumryq\"><code>paramsChange</code>：当路径或路径参数更改时重新运行警卫和解析器。这不包括查询参数。此选项是默认值。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bq5q7a6hw9sgt4xof8lu341az\"><code>always</code>：在每次执行时运行。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6tofwqw9w1ttj435p4wxk9d9f\"><code>pathParamsChange</code>：路径参数更改时重新运行保护器和解析器。这不会比较矩阵或查询参数。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5jr9b5y36guodwhftuuztpjbt\"><code>paramsOrQueryParamsChange</code>：在路径、矩阵或查询参数更改时运行。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e81g4ohsxvj4ijuutnz15fch1\"><code>pathParamsOrQueryParamsChange</code>：当路径参数更改或查询参数更改时，重新运行保护器和解析器。这不包括矩阵参数。</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router\n - api/router/OnSameUrlNavigation\n - api/router/Route\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/router\n - api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\n - api/router/Route#runGuardsAndResolvers\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#runguardsandresolvers\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#see-also\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/models.ts#L242-L267\n-->"}